text: Karsten Stenersen (born 24 September 1971) is a Norwegian former cyclist. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics, placing eleventh in the time trial. He is the brother of Bjørn Stenersen. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Norway Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bergen
